v 3
d splink: Probabilistic record linkage using the Fellegi-Sunter model
d
d Full-fidelity implementation matching the Python splink v4 package.
d Features: 19 comparison methods (JW, Jaro, Levenshtein, DL, Jaccard,
d exact, numeric, cosine, intersect, name, email, postcode, nameswap,
d dob, pctdiff, abs_date, abs_time, distance_km, custom), multiple
d blocking rules with OR logic, term frequency adjustments, EM training,
d supervised m-estimation, round-robin EM, clustering, salting,
d visualization commands, and cross-dataset linking.
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260306
d
